`#  $school: {{ request.query_dict.schools || '' }}`
```query MyQuery($school: [HS_Enum]) {
  CRM {
    p_&lt;custom_obj_name&gt;_collection(filter: {schools__in: $school}) {
      items {
        schools
      }
    }
  }
}```
This returns values in graphiql (with var set `{"school": "Harvard Law School"}` ) but not hubl graphql
